                     <interp inst="t18260914-432-person2242" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I was fetched, and took the prisoner with the property - she said she had not taken it; but afterwards said she was tipsy, and did not know what she had done, and begged for mercy.</p>
